HEADWORD: Dobson
<hw>Dob"son</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The
aquatic larva of a large neuropterous insect (<spn>Corydalus
cornutus</spn>), used as bait in angling. See
<er>Hellgamite</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dobule</ent>⟦br⟧
